longBusinessSummary: Incoming, Inc., through its subsidiary, North American Bio-Energies LLC, refines, produces, and distributes commercial-grade biodiesel from agri-based feedstock in the Southeast region of the United States. It also offers kerosene, de-methylated glycerin, and recovered methanol. The company sells its products directly or through wholesale distributors primarily to petroleum distributors, refiners, and manufacturers in North Carolina, South Carolina, and Virginia. Incoming, Inc. was founded in 2006 and is based in New York, New York.
